<h1 class="text-danger">ISHUB</h1>

<p>
    Welcome to <strong>ISHUB</strong> portal which is an application written by the IS Department to provide reporting, data analysis and data correction capabilities.
    The application contains pages which provide different features which are explained below:
</p>

<h2 class="text-danger">Ambrisentan REMS Submission</h2>

<ul>
    <li>This page is used to the change the status of transactions. The transactions can be marked as Accepted, Rejected or Deferred.</li>
    <li>Allows editting of external data for Ambrisentan and tracks which user made the change.</li>
</ul>

